{"tid":2498089,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"財經論壇｜地產股價值的迷思（丘卓文）","createTime":"2021-04-21T02:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T03:39:07.000Z","uid":24730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"401bfeafba3fcd099316e9ee50ce25d5358324c3","tid":2498089,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:33:19.000Z","msg":"財經論壇｜地產股價值的迷思（丘卓文）<br />\n10小時前<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210421/J6LFICGCMFDGHCO4DULRMSJAFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210421%2FJ6LFICGCMFDGHCO4DULRMSJAFI%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dN9ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=d8a768cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210421%2FJ6LFICGCMFDGHCO4DULRMSJAFI%2F&h=4b9fd82f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210421/J6LFICGCMFDGHCO4DULRMSJAFI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因工作關係，在過去多年都接觸過不少海外基金經理，有一道問題他們經常會問及的就是香港樓價高企，為什麼地產股的股價與十多年前高位比較，仍有一大段距離？為何地產股股價對資產淨值會出現這麼大的折讓？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">以藍籌地產股為例，股價對資產淨值普遍折讓超過四成、而二、三線地產股的折讓有時更高達七至八成。</span>以上情況出現是不是市場失效造成？不過，這種現象其實已出現了差不多十年，市場機制相信不可能長期失效。那麼是否分析員的估值過分樂觀，高估地產股的價值及盈利假設。我看這種說法看來不能完全成立，即使是個別分析員的估值比較進取，也不足以解釋為何股價持續出現這麼大的折讓。<br />\n<br />\n是否因為本港地產公司財務風險高，從而影響估值? 現實是本港地產商的財政狀況十分穩健，大部份藍籌地產股的資產負債比率仍低於25%，經常性租金收益亦很豐厚。<span class=\"red\">有人說，股票市場走先樓市九個月，地產股股價對資產淨值大幅折讓是否反映未來樓價下跌風險? 理論上是可以這樣說，但實際情況是就算本港房地產價格全線下跌10%，由於本港地產商的負債不高，對資產淨值的影響只是稍高於10%。除非市場持續預期大冧市，否則藍籌地產股的股價對資產淨值折讓不應高達四成。</span>"},{"pid":"2ca19e4dddec99182c1b726d7155faf0f9bab603","tid":2498089,"uid":155601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0a7d61f3ce98a9831b549997bf99772c7b982f","tid":2498089,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151d72650d7d5d39f5187814a096a10839ab7db9","tid":2498089,"uid":169697,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:34:34.000Z","msg":"咁仲唔快啲put爆地產股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1969920c64c06d3e1a04adcf63d3eb9cfef7e2b","tid":2498089,"uid":62020,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為收租估值低<br />\n作者知唔知自己講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n內房就相反<br />\n因為賣樓所以估值低<br />\n龍湖 新城因為收租多所以估值高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}